			'/gallery/photo_36.jpg', '/gallery/photo_37.jpg', '/gallery/photo_38.jpg',
			'/gallery/photo_39.jpg', '/gallery/photo_40.jpg'
		],
		about: [
			'We demystify the certification journey, providing the technical oversight needed to secure the industry’s most respected seals of quality.',
